<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>AnatomyEasy - Panel de Admin</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f0f8ff;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
    }
    .container {
      text-align: center;
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      max-width: 400px;
      width: 100%;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #2c3e50;
    }
    form {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }
    label {
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-size: 1.1em;
    }
    input {
      padding: 10px;
      margin-top: 5px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      width: 80%;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    button {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #fff;
      background-color: #3498db;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    button:hover {
      background-color: #2980b9;
    }
    .message {
      margin-top: 20px;
      color: #e74c3c;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      color: #888;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Panel de Administraci贸n</h1>
    <p>Inicia sesi贸n para gestionar la aplicaci贸n y los usuarios.</p>

    <form action="/admin/login" method="post">
      <label for="email">Email:</label>
      <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
      <label for="password">Password:</label>
      <input type="password" id="password" name="password" required>
      <button type="submit">Iniciar Sesi贸n</button>
    </form>
    <% if locals[:message] %>
      <p class="message"><%= locals[:message] %></p>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
